</style><svg style="display: none;"><defs id="MathJax_SVG_glyphs"></defs></svg><p><strong>Objective</strong> <br>
In this challenge, we're going to learn about the difference between a <em>class</em> and an <em>instance</em>; because this is an <em>Object Oriented</em> concept, it's only enabled in certain languages. Check out the <a href="/challenges/30-class-vs-instance/tutorial">Tutorial</a> tab for learning materials and an instructional video!  </p>
